sub_title: BSc Molecular Biology | MSc Evolutionary Biology
summary: A junior researcher in the field of molecular biology and evolution driven by scientific breakthroughs in speciation genetics/genomics, biodiversity, phylogenetics, conservation, and taxonomy. My expertise includes experimental design, data analysis and interpretation, academic writing and presenting, and various molecular genetic techniques and methods. My co-workers and fellow students have described me as a resourceful team player who keeps a proactive attitude and a healthy dose of humor when faced with challenging situations. I strive to be an empathetic listener and value authenticity. Apart from my professional endeavors, I take great pride in persistence, diligence, and compassion.
